	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Your will guides others like a fire in the dark. As a bonus action, you cause a small flame to hover over a willing creature within 60 feet for 1 hour. While marked the creature gains a bonus equal to your Constitution modifier on any Constitution Saving Throws it makes for the next hour.</p><p>The creature sheds bright light in a 10-foot radius and cannot be surprised.</p>",
